  <description><![CDATA[<p><strong>Sleeps: 6 Guests</strong></p>
<p>This charming chalet is located in the heart of the lovely old village of Val d’Isère, only a short stroll from the picturesque Church of St Bernard de Menthon. Tucked away in an old narrow lane, Les Barmettes enjoys a quiet location, yet all the amenities of the resort are right on the doorstep. The well-known après-ski and shops are within easy and tempting reach!</p>
<p>The chalet is ideal for a small group of friends or families looking for easy access to the slopes. The recently refurbished cosy lounge/dining area with a log burning fire and sunny south-facing balcony provides a lovely space to relax after a day skiing. The chalet is on the first floor of a traditional stone and wooden Savoyard building.</p>]]></description>
